Java Exercise:
Design a Java Menu driven CRUD code for any one of the collections given in the image. 
Eg Passengers Collection should be a collection of Passengers Class 
where passenger_id should be unique and required field.

The Menu should :
    Display all records  : forEach() of Stream API
    Get a particular record via ID : findAny().Else()
    Insert a record : Add()
    Delete a record : Remove()
    Update a record : filter according to ID/findAny(), use map() of Stream API to update


